cs.MA, cs.RO, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the emergence of language convention within a swarm of robots foraging in an open environment. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper involves the use of robots for the experiment. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is relevant as the paper investigates the emergence of language convention and naming of resources. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper involves the use of language games and explores the possibility of language emergence in a task-induced interaction network. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper involves the control of a swarm of robots foraging in an open environment.
